Definition: a document written by someone still legally capable requesting that he should be allowed to die if subsequently severely disabled or suffering terminal illness
Example: after he discovered he had AIDS he drew up a living will
Synonyms: legal_document, noun, group, law, c, a, document, written, by, someone, still, legally, capable, requesting, that, he, should, be, allowed, to, die, if, subsequently, severely, disabled, or, suffering, terminal, illness, after, discovered, had, AIDS, drew, up, living, will
Category: noun.communication
